dct_title_s: Map of Newfoundland to accompany the paper by the Revd. J. Moreton
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. From: Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 34 (1864), pp. 263-71; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.34 1864. Geographic coordinate grid was hand drawn after map was published.
